#. type: Plain text
msgid "Today we are starting a donation campaign to fund our work in 2017."
msgstr ""
"Avui comencem una campanya de donacions per finançar la nostra feina el 2017."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Unlike most other tools on the Internet, Tails comes for *free* as in "
"*freedom*. We are not selling your data, sending you targeted advertising, "
"nor will ever sell our project to a big company. We give out Tails for free "
"simply because everybody deserves to be protected from surveillance and "
"censorship. But also because being free software is a necessary requirement "
"for our tools to be safe, and protect you as intended. If our source code "
"was closed, there would be no way of actually verifying that our software is "
"trustworthy."
msgstr ""
"A diferència de la majoria d'altres eines d'Internet, Tails és *gratuït* i "
"és *Programari Lliure*. No venem les vostres dades, no us enviem publicitat "
"dirigida, ni vendrem mai el nostre projecte a una gran empresa. Donem Tails "
"de forma gratuïta simplement perquè tothom mereix estar protegit de la "
"vigilància i la censura. Però també perquè ser programari lliure és un "
"requisit necessari perquè les nostres eines estiguin segures i us "
"protegeixin com es pretén. Si es tanqués el nostre codi font, no hi hauria "
"manera de verificar que el nostre programari sigui fiable."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Since 2014, we raised 210'000€ on average each year, coming from:"
msgstr "Des de 2014, hem recaptat 210 000€ de mitjana cada any, procedents de:"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid "People like you"
msgstr "Gent com tu"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid "Private companies like Mozilla or DuckDuckGo"
msgstr "Empreses privades com Mozilla o DuckDuckGo"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid "Foundations and NGOs like Hivos and Access Now"
msgstr "Fundacions i ONGs com Hivos i Access Now"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Entities related to the US government like the Open Technology Fund (OTF)  "
"or the National Democratic Institute (NDI)"
msgstr ""
"Entitats relacionades amb el govern dels EUA com l'Open Technology Fund "
"(OTF) o el National Democratic Institute (NDI)"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[[!img income.png link=\"no\" class=\"top-margin center\" alt=\"Related to US\n"
"government: 34%, Foundations & NGOs: 34%, Individuals: 17%, Companies:\n"
"15%\"]]\n"
msgstr ""
"[[!img income.png link=\"no\" class=\"top-margin center\" alt=\"Relacionat amb el govern\n"
"dels EUA: 34%, Fundacions i ONG: 34%, Particulars: 17%, Empreses:\n"
"15%\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We often hear complaints about the fact that many software projects that are "
"meant to fight surveillance, like Tor and Tails, get a lot of funding from "
"the US government whose own surveillance projects are severely criticized. "
"We completely share this concern and we will worry about our accountability "
"and sustainability as long as the survival of our project depends on a few "
"small grants, some of them coming from organizations linked to governments."
msgstr ""
"Sovint sentim queixes sobre el fet que molts projectes de programari que "
"estan destinats a lluitar contra la vigilància, com Tor i Tails, reben molt "
"de finançament del govern dels Estats Units; els projectes de vigilància del "
"qual són durament criticats. Compartim completament aquesta preocupació i "
"ens preocuparem per la nostra responsabilitat i sostenibilitat sempre que la "
"supervivència del nostre projecte depengui d'unes petites subvencions, "
"algunes d'elles procedents d'organitzacions vinculades als governs."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Now, we would like you to think about it: where should our funding come from?"
msgstr "Ara, ens agradaria que penseu: d'on ha de venir el nostre finançament?"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The answer is clear to us: the survival of Tails should be guaranteed by our "
"users themselves, so that in return, we can continue to use our money in "
"their best interest, with complete independence."
msgstr ""
"La resposta és clara per a nosaltres: la supervivència de Tails l'han de "
"garantir els mateixos usuaris, de manera que, a canvi, puguem seguir "
"utilitzant els nostres diners en el seu millor interès, amb total "
"independència."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"From anonymized statistics on our website we know that Tails is used by "
"around 18 000 people every day. **If each of them gave 12€, the price of a "
"USB stick, our budget for the whole year would be raised within one day.** "
"As you can see, funding Tails through donations is a realistic and our "
"budget ridiculously small compared to the multibillionaire companies and "
"agencies running the surveillance business."
msgstr ""
"A partir de les estadístiques anònimes del nostre lloc web sabem que Tails "
"és utilitzat per unes 18 000 persones cada dia. **Si cadascuna d'elles donés "
"12€, el preu d'un llapis USB, el nostre pressupost per a tot l'any "
"s'assoliria en un dia.** Com podeu veure, finançar Tails a través de "
"donacions és realista i el nostre pressupost ridículament petit en "
"comparació a les empreses i agències multimilionàries que gestionen el "
"negoci de la vigilància."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"But many of our users could actually get in trouble if they donated to an "
"anti-surveillance tool like Tails. So when donating to Tails you are also "
"[[helping all of these people|news/who_are_you_helping]] by keeping Tails "
"alive. Please consider setting up a yearly or monthly donation."
msgstr ""
"Però molts dels nostres usuaris podrien tenir problemes si fessin una "
"donació a una eina antivigilància com Tails. Per tant, quan feu una donació "
"a Tails, també esteu [[ajudant a totes aquestes persones|news/"
"who_are_you_helping]] mantenint Tails viu. Penseu en configurar una donació "
"anual o mensual."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"If you want Tails to remain independent, please take one minute to make a "
"donation."
msgstr ""
"Si voleu que Tails es mantingui independent, preneu un minut per fer una "
"donació."

